  * `form-field-changed` {`CustomEvent<EventTarget | null>`} - 

  * `value-changed` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - 

  * `form-changed` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - 

Attributes:

  * `language` - 

  * `resources` - 

  * `schema` - 

  * `label` {`string`} - 

  * `value` - 

  * `error` - 

  * `wizard` {`boolean`} - 

  * `code-theme` {`string`} - the name of the code-editor theme

  * `autofocus` {`boolean`} - automatically set focus on the first field if that field has autofocus

